values: well nothing much going on here. just getting a bunch of shit down for school. and getting ready for a new year and all. whats up with all of you guys. i havent talked to any of you lately. tell me how your life is going. i am so tired. and i am getting sick. my throat and everything hurt so bad. i cant stand it. i am happy because i get to see anthony tomorrow. yay. even though i saw him a lot last week but i dont care because i love him so much!! hehe!! it has already been 2 months. yay!! i am happy about that. well i hope everyone else is doing good. dont mind my randomness. love ya all! happy new year!! ~min

because i know people that are saying shit behind my back. its like what the hell. if you have something to say, say it to my face. and that goes for all of you, if you ever have a problem with me then tell it to my face. it hurts more if you say it behind my back and dont tell me. and how am i going to know if you have a problem with me inless you tell me. have a great break. c ya later.

but i am a bit down because my dad didnt get this one job that i was hoping that he would get. it is really stressful for us, and i thought that he would get this one. he sent out a resamy for best buy and for something that he has done for years so i just hope that he gets it so we dont have so many problems. but otherwise im good. i am so hyper today. my mom is concerned about me. she heard my singing and right away she was worried...lol...im not that bad...well okay but yeah anywho....i hope you all have a wonderful christmas/break, and a happy new year. love ya all! :D peace!! ~minda
